COMMANDS

    Escape (ESCAPE / Esc)
        Quit the game

    (1), (F1)
        Switch to the SDL GUI

    (2), (F2)
        Switch to the SFML GUI

    (3), (F3)
        Switch to the Allegro GUI

    (P)
        Pause / Resume the music

    (+)
        increase the volume of the music

    (-)
        decrease the volume of the music

    GAME

        (F)
            Forfeit the current game.

        === Player 1 ===

            Up Arrow (↑)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the top of the board

            Right Arrow (←)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the right of the board

            Down Arrow (↓)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the bottom of the board

            Left Arrow (→)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the left of the board

            (E)
                Simulate the first player snake eating a +1 Bonus

        === Player 2 ===

            (Z)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the top of the board

            (Q)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the right of the board

            (S)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the bottom of the board

            (D)
                when possible, turn the Snake to go to the left of the board

            (R)
                Simulate the second player snake eating a +1 Bonus

